 our approach represents a useful step forward for\nCXR CAD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Sep 2020 18:50:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 2020 15:47:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2020 18:47:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-01"}
