ity field. The analyses show the important and urgent need of\nproper methodologies for a better definition of cables projected maintenance\ncosts and learning coefficients dedicated to network restructuring,\nreconfiguration and expansion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Sep 2020 07:58:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-15"}
