ed bipartite graph G with 2n vertices, we have that 0 \\leq gf(G)-Af(G)\n\\leq 1/2 (n-1)(n-2); For non-bipartite case, -1/2 (n^2-n-2) \\leq gf(G)-Af(G)\n\\leq (n-1)(n-2).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Sep 2020 08:19:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-08"}
